			<h4><a id="comment_link_64320347" name="comment_link_64320347" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23259523&amp;cid=64320347" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64320347)" >Can I mine the White House lawn</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64320347" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64320347); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>)</span></h4>
